{"tid":1191022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"六九上街　六十上班","createTime":"2019-06-07T16:39:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T15:32:48.000Z","uid":74058,"like":28,"dislike":70,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1b1093bd105bd477b2c12d10ef2a7522daadac09","tid":1191022,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T16:39:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea94e5530677d38f32bef10902498ff1d1b101c8","tid":1191022,"uid":74058,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T16:40:21.000Z","msg":"梁君彥：4項特別安排確保逃犯條例二讀和三讀順利<br />\n2019-06-06 HKT 19:28<br />\n立法會主席梁君彥表示，因應下星期三逃犯條例會恢復二讀和三讀，行管會在條例通過前，將有4項即時生效的特別安排，以確保會議順利進行。<br />\n<br />\n他說，除了秘書處安排導賞團外，立法會只接待不超過30名公眾人士旁聽，議員助理亦不可進入大樓的1樓至3樓，文件由收發組轉交議員。<br />\n<br />\n梁君彥補充，訪客可到有關議員辦公室的樓層及5樓，但午夜12時至翌日6時前就不能留在大樓，行管會亦同意會在1樓綠地毯設通道，供議員進出立法會會議廳。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1461352-20190606.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1461352-20190606.htm&d=Bm7f%2FS52JQW29R4IancW85Urr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=89cc29e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1461352-20190606.htm&h=e03da4e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1461352-20190606.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f58a5fb65697395ed715985d5af5b1749ac55b99","tid":1191022,"uid":40628,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T16:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LU3hjos.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLU3hjos.jpg&h=c4378950&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cefec61ecc40db59feee12e88e8f81459b7420ab","tid":1191022,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T16:42:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96d9d7b1a1e72aff55d63063003142ef6ffd920","t